<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037857" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute><rs type="person">N. B.</rs> Amico suo charissimo <rs type="person">F. C.</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Ecce hic paucis responsionem ad ultimas <rs type="letter">tuas suavissimas</rs> <rs type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> mihi traditas; volebam quidem statim
<lb/>ad eas rescribere, sed tempus mihi non permisit literas, quas revera jam inchoaveram, ad finem per<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ducere, quamobrem scriptionem hucusque differre coactus fui, quod te non admod<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre laturum
<lb/>spero, cum nihilominus sententiam meam circa conditionem per <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Debeyer</rs> nostratem tibi oblatam,
<lb/>ut petiisti, aperuerim <rs type="person">Raillardo</rs>, qui se eam tibi perscripsisse paulo ante abitum meum mihi affir<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>mavit. Intellexisti itaque ex <rs type="letter">literis</rs> <rs type="person">Raillardi</rs> et quidem, ut credo, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter opinionem, me conditio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nem istam tibi dissuadere, sed velim credas, istud consilium minime procedere ex aliquo contradicen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>di aut te <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> detinendi studio, sed potius ex su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o quo te complector amore, qui non permittit
<lb/>ut te in simile vel forte deterius, quam quod ego jam evasi, periculum conjicias. Si h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c conditio
<lb/>tantopere, ut <rs type="person">Schwartzius</rs> putat, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimanda esset, ego ipse eam arripuissem, nec illam repudi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>assent <rs type="person">Waldkirchius</rs>, <rs type="person">Crusius</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qui posterior tamen, si quisquam alius, causam habuisset eam
<lb/>acceptandi<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> et alii plures; hoc unicum tibi sufficiat, ut eam similiter detrectes. Rationes spe<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>cialiores si desideras, eas inclusa schedula continet. Dicis quidem homines esse in su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o dignita<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tis et honoris gradu constitutos, quos fidem fallere non sit probabile, sed ne mireris, si dicam,
<lb/>me in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedentibus meis <rs type="letter">literis</rs>, in quibus scripsi, solenne esse Bernensibus sub variis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>textibus
<lb/>promissa fallere, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue hos intellexisse, adeo ut non dubitem, ipsum <abbr>D. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Battierium</rs> et <rs type="person">Nic.
<lb/>Schwartzium</rs>, si rei statum exactius cognoverint, consilium mutaturos esse. Si tamen magis ad<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>huc in rem inquirendam esse putes, optime ages, si <rs type="person">Raillardo</rs> scribes, sunt enim <rs type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> duo
<lb/>studiosi Theologi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Bernenses <rs type="person">Sprünglinus</rs> et <rs type="person">Risoldus</rs>, juvenes admodum probi et eruditi, et
<lb/>amici nostri singulares, qui <rs type="person">Raillardo</rs> rem omnem candide aperient; imo ipse <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Debe<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>r</rs> et <abbr>D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs type="person">Waldkirch</rs>, quem nunc credo <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> degere, si sincere loqui volunt, tibi consilium dare pote<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>runt, habuimus enim <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Waldkirch</rs>, <rs type="person">Crusius</rs> et ego singulis fere diebus conventicula nostra 
<pb facs="1037858" n="2"/> 
<lb/>in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Debeyer</rs>, ubi non semel de ipsa hac conditione verba fecimus. Quicquid sit, noli fe<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>stinare, nam occasionem hanc tibi nunquam, nedum post duos vel tres annos, elapsuram esse
<lb/>persuasus sum. Audivi de infelici obitu <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Me<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>eri</rs>, qui me, ut facile judicare potes, ma<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>gnopere afflixit; audivi etiam de promotione <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Fre<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice></rs>, cum quo in tam sublimi loco nunc
<lb/>constituto vereor ut mihi amplius colloquendi facultas sit; <rs type="person">adgnatum</rs> quoque ejus Professi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>onem extraordinariam tot machinationibus extorquere velle indignabundus percepi, vix
<lb/>enim est ut hominem ob eruditionem suam tanto fastu turgentem magni <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimare possim.
  <lb/>Quomodo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-122123158">Grundlerus</rs> <rs type="biblio">Dissertationem</rs> suam defenderit, et an adhuc <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> sit scire aveo.
<lb/>S<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>d tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quid agunt Mus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>? nuntia mihi qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, an Examen jam sustinueris, an <rs type="biblio">Disserta<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem</rs> jam conscripseris, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipua sint illius contenta, et qua methodo illam tra<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>ctes; spero me sub finem sequentis mensis, ut jam scripsi, domi futurum, tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que <rs type="biblio">Disputa<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tioni</rs> interfuturum esse, ubi mihi si non Actoris saltem auditoris partes promitto. Fini<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rem hic literas meas, nisi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipuum, de quo te monendum esse duxi, restaret; moneo
<lb/>te nempe et rogo, imo per amicitiam nostram sancte obtestor, ut tandem de beneficiis
<lb/>tibi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me exhibitis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nulla sunt, sileas nec tua erga me merita amplius extenues,
<lb/>satis enim scio, quam proficua mihi sit amicitia tua, quantos ex ea fructus hucusque
<lb/>tulerim et in posterum sperare possim; desine, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, locutionibus istis h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolicis os
<lb/>mihi obturare, nec crede me tam vanum esse, ut spes et refugium tuum audire malim,
<lb/>tribuas hoc epitheton Deo <choice><abbr>O. M.</abbr><expan>Optimum Maximum</expan></choice> cui soli debetur; ego amici nomine, quo nullum aliud
<lb/>majus et gratius esse existimo, contentus ero.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Parisiis</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-07-12">12. Julii 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
